  "detailed_description": "Tale's Casino Escape is a real time combat adventure RPG. All the qualities of a good RPG have been combined and applied at Tale's Casino Escape.<br><br><strong><u>FEATURES:</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/b8b918e7174d59aba35d04b8e85dce34.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- EVERY enemie can be your ally. By killing an enemy, you have a small chance of dropping it´s sphere. If you get it, you can use it to fight with you!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/8d47209ffa5d85bf819cec0bf936dfc1.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/a2ce82abb6952a07bb9df64d29152fa6.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- Collect stars and unlock new stages! <br>Each stage has some quests to complete, for each completed quest you get a star!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/3cc62f1c2a511a3ac96b2accd3ccb068.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/9075da62047bf6b2b8173488e61d74cc.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/5edd5735b0396ae068b1ff4df6265757.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- Like every good RPG, the game is full of hidden things! You will have to beat puzzles and have logical thinking to find them.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/59077f9d07e814a0204ee77fef4b7810.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- As said above, the game is challenging. You will have to think of several solutions if you want to complete the game 100%.<br><u>*If you do not like puzzles, and logical thinking mini games, do not worry, you can play the game until the end without having to beat these types of challenges</u>.</strong><br><br><strong><u>STORY:</u></strong><br><br>Once upon a time there was a girl who worked in a casino. She worked so hard, that she couldn't even leave the casino. In fact she was a prisoner.<br><br>So, one day, a great idea comes to her mind. She decides to ESCAPE!!!<br><br>Then, on a dark and cold night, she gets out of bed, and in light steps she begins to execute her master plan, ESCAPE FROM THE CASINO.",
  "about_the_game": "Tale's Casino Escape is a real time combat adventure RPG. All the qualities of a good RPG have been combined and applied at Tale's Casino Escape.<br><br><strong><u>FEATURES:</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/b8b918e7174d59aba35d04b8e85dce34.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- EVERY enemie can be your ally. By killing an enemy, you have a small chance of dropping it´s sphere. If you get it, you can use it to fight with you!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/8d47209ffa5d85bf819cec0bf936dfc1.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/a2ce82abb6952a07bb9df64d29152fa6.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- Collect stars and unlock new stages! <br>Each stage has some quests to complete, for each completed quest you get a star!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/3cc62f1c2a511a3ac96b2accd3ccb068.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/9075da62047bf6b2b8173488e61d74cc.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/5edd5735b0396ae068b1ff4df6265757.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- Like every good RPG, the game is full of hidden things! You will have to beat puzzles and have logical thinking to find them.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149930/extras/59077f9d07e814a0204ee77fef4b7810.avif?t=1727918266\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>- As said above, the game is challenging. You will have to think of several solutions if you want to complete the game 100%.<br><u>*If you do not like puzzles, and logical thinking mini games, do not worry, you can play the game until the end without having to beat these types of challenges</u>.</strong><br><br><strong><u>STORY:</u></strong><br><br>Once upon a time there was a girl who worked in a casino. She worked so hard, that she couldn't even leave the casino. In fact she was a prisoner.<br><br>So, one day, a great idea comes to her mind. She decides to ESCAPE!!!<br><br>Then, on a dark and cold night, she gets out of bed, and in light steps she begins to execute her master plan, ESCAPE FROM THE CASINO.",
